name: TrendingTopics
0:
”Alexa, ask trending topics”
”What's trending in Hacker News ?”
”Current trending topics in Tech Meme”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: trending topics
des: One stop for all your favorite trending tech topics. Currently supports Hacker News, Tech Crunch and Tech Meme. For sure, more will be added based on the response. Note that this is unofficial app which pulls the information from the RSS feeds
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
